## Modules

### Chosen Modules and Point Calculation

| Module | Type | Points | Team Member(s) | Why It Was Chosen | How It Was Implemented |
|------|------|------:|------|------|------|
| Frontend + Backend Frameworks | Major | 2 | `ebelkadi`, `ysbai-jo`, `msennane`, `sennakhl` | The project needs a full user-facing platform with admin and API layers | React/Vite frontend plus Go backend |
| Database + ORM | Major | 2 | `msennane`, `sennakhl` | The domain is relational and data-heavy | PostgreSQL + GORM models and migrations |
| REST API Design | Major | 2 | `msennane`, `sennakhl` | The frontend and admin panels depend on a stable service contract | `/v1/...` route family across auth, workouts, nutrition, admin, and AI |
| Authentication + Security | Major | 2 | `msennane`, `sennakhl`, `ebelkadi` | The project contains private health-related user data | JWT access/refresh flow, protected routes, 2FA, middleware |
| Internationalization | Major | 2 | `ebelkadi`, `ysbai-jo` | The platform targets multilingual users and requires Arabic support | English/French/Arabic message catalogs and RTL support |
| Responsive Frontend | Major | 2 | `ebelkadi`, `ysbai-jo` | The main product target is mobile-first use | custom CSS, mobile layouts, adaptive admin/user screens |
| WebSocket Realtime | Major | 2 | `msennane`, `ebelkadi` | Admin metrics benefit from live updates | `GET /v1/admin/dashboard/realtime` + frontend socket hook |
| Monitoring | Major | 2 | `msennane` | The backend stack needs observability | Prometheus + Grafana + metrics middleware |
| Data Export | Major | 2 | `msennane`, `sennakhl`, `ebelkadi` | Users should be able to retrieve their own data | export endpoints and frontend export handling |
| Notifications | Major | 2 | `msennane`, `sennakhl`, `ebelkadi` | Engagement and reminders are part of the product loop | notification services, endpoints, and frontend center |
| AI Integration | Major | 2 | `msennane`, `sennakhl`, `ebelkadi` | Coaching and Q&A are central differentiators | `/v1/chat`, history, feedback, coach-summary |
| Testing | Minor | 1 | all | Validation is needed across frontend and backend changes | Go tests, Vitest, RTL, MSW |

### Total

- **Major modules:** `11 x 2 = 22`
- **Minor modules:** `1 x 1 = 1`
- **Total:** `23 points`

These modules were chosen because they directly support the delivered product instead of being added only to increase the score. Each one corresponds to an actual visible or testable part of the platform.

