## Notes and Limitations

- The current realtime layer is focused on the admin dashboard only
- The frontend depends on both the Go API and the exercise library service
- Some earlier planning documents describe aspirational architecture; the repository implementation is the source of truth
- The project is feature-rich and integration-heavy, so merges and API/frontend alignment were recurring project challenges
